    <text type="letter">
        <body>
                <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.01109.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
                <opener>
                    <salute>Walt,</salute>
                </opener>
            <p>Here is one soul, born in the year of meteors '59,<ptr target="loc.01109_n1"/> who, 
                most unutterably has, in these last 3&#189; years, received the shock of thy influence.</p>
                <p>Welcome to Britain!&#8212;especially to North Britain!&#8212;most especially to the 
                    foreground of my own certain centre of identity: we will cross orbits.<ptr target="loc.01109_n2"/></p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Unmistakably yours,</salute>
                    <signed>J.J. Brown.</signed>
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>160 Cathcart R<hi rend="underline">d</hi>; Glasgow,</addrLine>
                        <addrLine><hi rend="underline">Scotland</hi>.</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Walt Whitman.</addrLine>
                        <addrLine><hi rend="underline">United States.</hi> America</addrLine>
                    </address>
                </closer> 
            <note type="authorial" place="rightmargin">&#8212;The Great Camerado is here! The Lover True 
                for whom we pine, He is <hi rend="underline">here!!</hi><ptr target="loc.01109_n4"/></note>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.01109.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
